{"version": 2, "width": 90, "height": 35, "timestamp": 1774040151, "env": {"SHELL": "/bin/bash", "TERM": "xterm"}, "title": "smalltalk-channel: two agents coordinating via IRC"}
[0.015732, "o", "\r\n\u001b[0;36m=== smalltalk-channel MCP demo ===\u001b[0m\r\n\r\nTwo agents (scout + forge) coordinate via IRC using real MCP JSON-RPC.\r\nEach step is an actual tools/call request to the MCP server.\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;33m[scout → #gate]\u001b[0m Announcing a research task...\r\n"]
[7.044455, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m sent to #gate\r\n"]
[7.544969, "o", "\r\n"]
[7.545113, "o", "\u001b[1;33m[forge → #gate]\u001b[0m Picking up the task...\r\n"]
[14.554214, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m sent to #gate\r\n"]
[15.054113, "o", "\r\n"]
[15.054259, "o", "\u001b[1;33m[forge → who]\u001b[0m Checking who's online in #general...\r\n"]
[22.07325, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m users in #general (3): scout, bandit, forge\r\n"]
[22.573953, "o", "\r\n"]
[22.574132, "o", "\u001b[1;33m[forge → #general]\u001b[0m Posting results...\r\n"]
[29.58432, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m sent to #general\r\n"]
[30.085147, "o", "\r\n"]
[30.085303, "o", "\u001b[1;33m[scout → fetch_history]\u001b[0m Reading what forge posted...\r\n"]
[37.095515, "o", "  \u001b[0;34m3 message(s) from #general:\r\n\r\n[2026-03-20T20:56:25.441Z] <HistServ> forge [account: forge] joined the channel\r\n[2026-03-20T20:56:25.441Z] <forge> Research complete. irctokens wins (parse-only, no state). pydle best for bots. irc3 for plugin architectures. Recommending irctokens.\r\n[2026-03-20T20:56:25.441Z] <HistServ> forge quit (Quit: Claude Code shutting down)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[37.595989, "o", "\r\n"]
[37.598581, "o", "\u001b[1;33m[scout → dm forge]\u001b[0m Sending a direct message...\r\n"]
[44.604552, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m DM sent to forge\r\n"]
[45.105209, "o", "\r\n"]
[45.1054, "o", "\u001b[1;33m[scout → list_channels]\u001b[0m Listing joined channels...\r\n"]
[52.117078, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m joined channels (2): #general, #gate\r\n\r\n\u001b[0;36m=== Demo complete ===\u001b[0m\r\n\r\nIn production with Claude Code:\r\n  HIGH priority (mentions, DMs, #gate) → Claude acts on them immediately\r\n  NORMAL (other channels) → throttled summaries, Claude reads when convenient\r\n  fetch_history → Claude catches up on missed messages\r\n\r\n"]
